# PASS: 3 total, 3 pass, 0 fail, 0 error, 0 skip, 0 todo, 0 only\.

Finished in 4209 ms w/TSH exec time of 104 ms\.
.fi
.RE
.SH TIBET SHELL
.P
This command invokes the client\-side TIBET Shell to run a TSH script/command\.
